text: my card had problem exiting so it ended up entering without exiting, i went to the counter the person was using her phone. had to call out multiple time as i had class in 5mins and she didn’t hear until i raised my voice saying “hi” she then roll her eyes and banged my card on the table.
Good MRT Station, can go to Singapore Poly directly.

This MRT station is futuristic looking with so much potential in the coming years. With the new estate under construction, it is shaping up to be another point of attraction for tourists to come when exploring Singapore.

However, the station does feel like its in the middle of nowhere, with the roads surrounding the station.
to switch sides I had to go down to level two and then go to the other platform, which I found inefficient

Unique MRT station within green line, as the tracks are located in the middle of the station. Historically this station was built later after the network line established, explaining why the tracks are kept straight when approaching the station. It is a modern station, and has a toilet in the ticket concourse level.
